'''Jade Mills''' is an American [[real estate agent]], president of Jade Mills Estates, and the International Ambassador for Coldwell Banker Previews. In 2012, Mills became the #1 real estate agent worldwide for [[Coldwell Banker]], with over $360 million in sales. Mills' clients include [[Hollywood]] celebrities like [[Britney Spears]], [[Jennifer Aniston]], [[Charlie Sheen]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/morganbrennan/2012/05/21/homes-of-the-worlds-most-powerful-celebrities/#79e6bafe1136|title=Homes Of The World's Most Powerful Celebrities|work=forbes.com}}</ref><ref name="hollywoodreporter.com"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://la.curbed.com/2013/2/1/10278404/top-agent-jade-mills-dishes-tales-of-selling-to-the-superwealthy|title=Top Agent Jade Mills Dishes Tales of Selling to the Super Rich|work=curbed.com|first1=Adrian|last1=Glick Kudler|date=2013-02-01|access-date=2017-10-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/real-estate-runs-in-the-family-1459432408|title=Real Estate Runs in the Family|work=wsj.com|access-date=2017-10-30|date=2016-03-31|first1=Alina|last1=Dizik}}</ref> and [[Sela Ward]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://therealdeal.com/la/2016/03/01/jade-mills-on-listing-sela-wards-home-and-her-least-favorite-customers/|title=Jade Mills on listing Sela Ward’s home and her least favorite customers|work=therealdeal.com}}</ref>
Mills' first sale was a home for $42,000 in [[Van Nuys]].<ref name="hollywoodreporter.com"/> She has appeared on [[Bloomberg TV]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/b/f4f2a0b5-f623-48ce-9dfa-a7b161ff8f4c|title=$34 Million and Rising: Beverly Hills Feels No Pain|work=bloomberg.com|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806151214/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/b/f4f2a0b5-f623-48ce-9dfa-a7b161ff8f4c|archivedate=2016-08-06|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/b/f732fbb9-7c4a-4193-b9d1-7554d29e5cf3|title=What the Wealthy Want in Real Estate|work=bloomberg.com|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806204610/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/b/f732fbb9-7c4a-4193-b9d1-7554d29e5cf3|archivedate=2016-08-06|df=}}</ref> and [[Fox News]] as a real estate expert.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/leisure/2011/06/05/how-celebs-buy-homes-in-secret/|title=How celebs buy homes in secret|work=foxnews.com}}</ref> She serves as a board member for the Beverly Hills Chamber of Commerce<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.beverlyhillschamber.com/about/the-board/|title=Beverly Hills Chamber of Commerce 2016 – 2017 Board of Directors|work=beverlyhillschamber.com}}</ref> and on the Board of Governors at [[Cedars Sinai Hospital]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.topagentmagazine.com/top-real-estate-agent-in-california-jade-mills/|title=Top real estate agent in California Jade Mills|work=topagentmagazine.com}}</ref>
